// Test: code refers "stage" | Test# within class | Cannonball target # | Birdman time-of-day
//  Vehicle─▶      0           1          2                3          4          5           6
//           ┌───────────┬───────────┬───────────┐   ┌───────────┬──────────┬──────────┐┌─────────┐
